IVOV: Vanguard S&P Mid-Cap 400 Value Index Fund

The fund employs an indexing investment approach designed to track the performance of the S&P MidCap 400Â® Value Index, which represents the value companies, as determined by the index sponsor, of the S&P MidCap 400 Index.
